    "name": "La Siesta Hoi An Resort & Spa",
    "detail": "Although the weather did not behave for our stay in Hoi An our stay was made memorable by this hotel. Fantastically friendly and helpful staff, clean and comfortable room, stunning pool and tasty breakfast with a surprising amount of vegetarian options for Vietnam! We also enjoyed happy hour cocktails playing pool whilst we hid from the rain. The hotel itself is a 10-15 minute walk from the old town but there is a free shuttle bus and free bike hire (plus very cheap taxis) if you don’t fancy the walk. I also had a brilliant experience at the spa. All round just a lovely hotel! ",
